Module  : Hide Cancel In Editor
Version : 1.0.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This mod hides the cancel button in all posting editor screens.

Install:
--------

- Install this file in the directory "mods" within your
  Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Hide Cancel In Editor".

